data.description: Beautifully remodeled duplex in the heart of Los Angeles! Front unit is 3 bedrooms, 1 bath rents for $2,900 and the back unit is 2 bedrooms, 2 baths rents for $2,500. Back unit is a new construction ADU built in 2021.  Great opportunity to buy as an investment property or live in one and rent the other!  One of the units can be delivered vacant before the close of escrow or with tenants.  Both units have their own laundry rooms, open floor plans, quartz counter tops and individual yards.  No rent control!  Seller has an FHA loan with 2.9% interest rate that could be assumed by the buyer.  Please do not disturb tenants or go to the property without appointment.
